from%20protesting%20against%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20demonstrations%20weren't%20only%20about%20the%20third-richest%20man%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20about%20pushing%20back%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20Venice%20as%20a%20theme%20park%20and%20playground%20for%20billionaires%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20living%20city%20that's%20home%20to%2050%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20historic%20center%20who%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20impacts%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-visiting-venice-overtourism-off-season-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emass%20tourism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20use%20Venice%20as%20a%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20Tommaso%20Cacciari%2C%20a%20Venetian%20activist%20and%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20No%20Space%20for%20Bezos%20movement%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20the%20billionaire%20Amazon%20founder.%20%26quot%3BWe%20used%20him%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20real%20problems%20of%20Venice%2C%20and%20it%20worked%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20glad%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-lauren-sanchez-wedding-protests-venice-photos-overtourism-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotests%20in%20Venice%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20headlines%20around%20the%20world%20this%20month%20as%20the%20city%2C%20which%20welcomes%2020%20million%20visitors%20annually%2C%20prepared%20for%20private%20jets%20and%20megayachts%20to%20arrive%2C%20carrying%20A-listers%20like%20the%20Kardashian-Jenner%20clan%20and%20Bill%20Gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20wedding%2C%20protesters%20gathered%20in%20a%20Venetian%20town%20square%20and%20along%20the%20iconic%20Rialto%20Bridge%2C%20holding%20signs%20that%20read%2C%20among%20other%20slogans%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20space%20for%20Bezos%26quot%3B%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20rocke