-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanti-tourism%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI%20has%20previously%20reported%2C%20including%20targeted%20demonstrations%20against%20companies%20like%20Airbnb.%20The%20palpable%20frustration%20felt%20by%20locals%20over%20overcrowded%20streets%2C%20environmental%20damage%2C%20and%20rising%20living%20costs%20has%20dissuaded%20some%20tourists%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-wont-go-back-to-venice-italy-over-tourism-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereturning%20to%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Fyall%2C%20the%20Visit%20Orlando%20endowed%20chair%20of%20tourism%20marketing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20Rosen%20College%20of%20Hospitality%20Management%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20Bezos-S%C3%A1nchez%20wedding%20protests%20showed%20how%20fed%20up%20Venetians%20are%20with%20overtourism%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFyall%20said%20the%20number%20of%20wedding%20guests%20was%20not%20necessarily%20the%20problem.%20But%20given%20the%20persistent%20problems%20of%20overtourism%20and%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20locals%20%26quot%3Bsee%20it%20as%20a%20little%20bit%20crass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protesters%20gather%20in%20Venice%20to%20demonstrate%20against%20%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20wedding.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6860987c85e81483682d01a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20gather%20in%20Venice%20to%20demonstrate%20against%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20wedding.%3Cp%3EPierfrancesco%20Celada%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-lauren-sanchez-wedding-protests-venice-photos-overtourism-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotesters%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20something%20like%2C%20'This%20is%20feeding%20into%20the%20image%2