e%2C%20I%20can%20firmly%20say%20that%20you%20won't%20have%20a%20problem%20storing%20enough%20food%20for%20a%20whole%20family%20in%20this%20fridge.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CFlex%20Drawer%20and%20inside%20of%20the%20Samsung%20French%20door%20refrigerator.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fcaec9ef1e50018f93db3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20can't%20recommend%20this%20fridge%20enough.%20It's%20spacious%2C%20easy%20to%20maintain%2C%20and%20energy-efficient.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20French%20Door%204-Door%20refrigerator%20in%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F612fca5a12b9cc001963bd30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20highly%20recommend%20it%20to%20anyone%20who's%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20fridge.%20If%20this%20size%20isn't%20quite%20right%20for%20your%20kitchen%2C%20check%20out%20the%20other%20options.%20They%20come%20in%20different%20widths%2C%20capacities%2C%20and%20depths%20to%20fit%20a%20variety%20of%20kitchens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231806c6b-fae2-4764-b51b-13f2ef32d8d4%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-50157-20%26h%3D3784b9d05dc949fbe967612bb9bcb0e404dd644f514e943fc3312ec2bd440a73%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f4354f%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fsamsung-french-4-door-refrigerator-flex-drawer-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Fhome-appliances%252Frefrigerators%252F4-door-french-door%252F28-cu--ft--4-door-f