7210996f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20GPS%20tracking%5C%22%3EBest%20GPS%20tracking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGPS%20trackers%20are%20a%20smart%20choice%20for%20cats%20who%20spend%20time%20outdoors%20or%20for%20indoor-only%20cats%20who%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20darting%20outside.%20However%2C%20devices%20with%20limited%20range%2C%20such%20as%20those%20that%20rely%20solely%20on%20Bluetooth%2C%20can%20only%20track%20your%20cat%20when%20you're%20nearby.%20With%20connectivity%20through%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20Verizon%2C%20and%20T-Mobile%20LTE%20networks%2C%20Tractive%20GPS%20offers%20real-time%20location%20tracking%2C%20so%20long%20as%20it's%20in%20an%20area%20with%20cellular%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20cat%20goes%20missing%2C%20Tractive's%20wide%20coverage%20pinpoints%20their%20location%20on%20a%20street%20map.%20A%20radar%2C%20on-collar%20sound%2C%20and%20built-in%20light%20can%20help%20you%20zero%20in%20on%20their%20location%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20hiding.%20Within%20Bluetooth%20range%2C%20the%20companion%20app's%20radar%20shows%20when%20you're%20getting%20closer%20to%20or%20farther%20from%20the%20tracker.%20This%2C%20along%20with%20a%20manually%20activated%20sound%2C%20allowed%20us%20to%20find%20the%20tracker%20tucked%20beneath%20a%20bush%20in%20the%20backyard%20with%20little%20effort.%20Although%20the%20sound%20is%20no%20louder%20than%20a%20bird%20chirp%2C%20it%20may%20startle%20an%20already%20frightened%20cat.%20That's%20why%20we%20especially%20appreciate%20the%20small%20light%20that%20can%20be%20turned%20on%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20black%20and%20white%20cat%20wearing%20the%20light%20blue%20Tractive%20pet%20tracker%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Tractive%20app%20showing%20the%20cat's%20path%20through%20a%20neighborhood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c15df748d8c055f4a5ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tractive%20Smart%20Cat%20Collar%20is%20an%20excellent%20way%20to%20monitor%20your%20cat's%20activity%20outdoors.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20received%20an%20alert%20right%20away%20when%20the%20GPS%20left%20the%20customizable%20safe%20zone%20around%20our%20house%20or%20entered%20the%20no-go%20zone%2C%20such%20as%20near%20a%20busy%20road.%20However%2C%20the%20smallest%20possible%20fence%20spans%20about%20600%20square%20feet.%20By%20the%20time%20we're%20notified%2C%20our%20cat%20will%20already%20be%20down%20the%20next%20block.%20Those%20who%20want%20to%20see%20their%20cat's%20typical%20hangouts%20can%20view%20the%20hot%20spot%20map.%20Frequently%20visited%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20park%20near%20our%20home%20%E2%80%94%20are%20highlighted%20in%20red.%20These%20are%20the%20first%20places%20we'd%20look%20for%20our%20cat%20if%20the%20GPS%20died%20or%20the%20collar%20fell%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20Tractive%20on%20daily%20on%201-%20to%202-mile%20walks%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%20before%20recharging.%20If%20your%20cat%20spends%20most%20of%20their%20time%20away%20from%20WiFi%2C%20and%20therefore%20out%20of%20battery-saving%20mode%2C%20battery%20life%20will%20be%20shorter%20but%20still%20reliable.%20You%20can%20conserve%20battery%20by%20adjusting%20location%20updates%20to%20every%205%2C%2015%2C%2030%2C%20or%2060%20minutes%20rather%20than%20using%20live%20tracking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETractive%20also%20functions%20somewhat%20like%20a%20feline%20FitBit%2C%20tracking%20your%20cat's%20sleep%2C%20activity%20levels%2C%20and%20estimated%20calories%20burned.%20Tractive's%20latest%20design%20is%20lighter%20and%20slimmer%20than%20when%20we%20first%20tested%20it.%20It%20weighs%20under%20an%20ounce%20and%20measures%20just%202.2%20inches%20%E2%80%94%20about%20the%20length%20of%20a%20house%20key.%20You%20almost%20miss%20it%20hiding%20under%20the%20fur%20of%20our%20floofiest%20cat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5c74c41-75c8-41a1-9864-0c6191653cca%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20calming%5C%22%3EBest%20calming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECalming%20collars%20for%20cats%20are%20designed%20to%20help%20ease%20stress%20during%20major%20changes%20like%20moving%2C%20traveling%2C%20or%20introducing%20a%20new%20baby.%20They%20may%20also%20help%20curb%20behaviors%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fhow-to-stop-cat-from-scratching-couch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escratching%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20urine%20marking%2C%20and%20tension%20between%20cats%20in%20multi-pet%20homes.%20Calming%20collars%20work%20by%20releasing%20synthetic%20pheromones%2C%20species-specific%20chemical%20signals%20that%20are%20odorless%20to%20humans%20but%20detectable%20to%20cats.%20Cats%20deposit%20facial%20pheromones%20by%20rubbing%20their%20chin%2C%20cheeks%2C%20and%20forehead%20on%20objects%20and%20people%20in%20areas%20they%20visit%20often.%20When%20they%20return%20and%20detect%20these%20pheromones%2C%20it%20can%20help%20them%20feel%20more%20secure.%20%26quot%3BThis%20reassuring%20response%20can%20also%20be%20triggered%20in%20adult%20cats%20with%20the%20use%20of%20synthetic%20pheromones%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feverycat.org%2Fabout%2Four-staff-and-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Maggie%20Placer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20veterinary%20science%20program%20manager%20at%20EveryCat%20Health%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recommend%20the%20Comfort%20Zone%20Calming%20Pheromone%20Collar%20for%20Cats.%20It's%20heat-activated%2C%20releasing%20calming%20pheromones%20when%20warmed%20by%20your%20cat's%20body%20heat%20that%20typically%20last%20up%20to%2030%20days.%20While%20the%20collar%20is%20odorless%20to%20people%2C%20it%20did%20leave%20a%20chalky%20residue%20on%20our%20fingers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%26quot%3Bbloom%26quot%3B%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20packaging%2C%20signals%20the%20pheromones%20are%20being%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20plastic%20ComfortZone%20calming%20collar%20and%20a%20gray%20and%20white%20cat%20wearing%20the%20same%20white%20collar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c28c85e81483682d0d43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20simply%20designed%20calming%20collar%20from%20Comfort%20Zone%20can%20remain%20effective%20for%20up%20to%2030%20days.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlacer%20recommends%20introducing%20calming%20pheromones%20at%20least%2048%20hours%20before%20a%20stressful%20event.%20The%20collar%20secures%20like%20a%20watch%20band%2C%20so%20it%20stays%20snug%20without%20flopping%20or%20sticking%20out.%20In%20an%20emergency%2C%20pressure%20on%20the%20collar%20causes%20the%20ridges%20to%20break%20free%20and%20the%20buckle%20to%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c588f0a-5361-4152-8d74-1cd0f41795c5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20bow%20tie%5C%22%3EBest%20bow%20tie%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmooth%2C%20lightweight%20materials%20like%20nylon%20are%20usually%20a%20good%20pick%20for%20collars%2C%20while%20cotton%20can%20be%20gentler%20on%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20Cahn%20says.%20Made%20by%20Cleo's%20stylish%20cat%20collars%20combine%20both%3A%20a%20cotton%20top%20layer%20and%20a%20flexible%2C%20densely%20woven%20nylon%20webbing%20underneath%20for%20durability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20by%20Cleo%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20collars%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.madebycleo.com%2Fcollections%2Fbow-tie-collar-sets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassic%20bow%20tie%20sets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20bunny%20ear%20designs%20that%20have%20the%20chic%20look%20of%20a%20French-tied%20scarf.%20We%20loved%20the%20look%20and%20quality%20of%20both%2C%20but%20ultimately%20found%20the%20bunny%20ear%20set%20to%20be%20the%20most%20comfortable%20for%20our%20feline%20testers.%20The%20bunny%20ears%20drape%20slightly%20like%20a%20scarf%2C%20while%20the%20classic%20bow%20ties%20can%20feel%20a%20bit%20stiff%20and%20bump%20against%20the%20chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22made%20by%20cleo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c3023d5881a51c1c5ec1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bunny%20Ear%20Bow%20collar%20set%20from%20Made%20By%20Cleo%20earned%20the%20comfort%20seal%20of%20approval%20from%20Leeson's%20two%20cats.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20Made%20by%20Cleo%20apart%20from%20other%20bow%20tie%20collar%20brands%20is%20the%20wide%20selection%20of%20styles%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20patterns%2C%20all%20inspired%20by%20the%20maker's%20cat%2C%20Cleo.%20Everything%20is%20crafted%20in%20its%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20studio%2C%20and%20you%20can%20customize%20your%20cat's%20look%20with%20gold%20or%20silver%20hardware%20and%20a%20matching%20removable%20bell.%20You%20can%20even%20add%20decorative%20charms%2C%20though%20Cahn%20says%20heavier%20collars%20or%20bulky%20tags%20may%20be%20less%20comfortable%20for%20cats.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20some%20cats%20and%20people%20may%20find%20charms%20too%20noisy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0fed470-0722-4f45-835e-9648b1cd9bfb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20personalized%5C%22%3EBest%20personalized%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20personalized%5C%22%3EIn%20addition%20to%20microchipping%2C%20Cahn%20recommends%20adding%20an%20ID%20tag%20to%20your%20cat's%20collar.%20%26quot%3BIf%20your%20kitty%20ever%20gets%20lost%2C%20having%20as%20many%20forms%20of%20identification%20as%20possible%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20may%20help%20them%20be%20returned%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbondvet.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gabrielle%20Fadl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20medical%20director%20at%20Bond%20Vet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cats%20are%20sensitive%20to%20the%20weight%20or%20sounds%20of%20dangling%20tags%2C%20and%20noisy%20tags%20can%20be%20annoying%20for%20cat%20parents%2C%20too.%20A%20personalized%20collar%20with%20your%20info%20printed%20directly%20on%20it%20can%20be%20more%20comfortable.%20The%20Frisco%20Polyester%20Personalized%20Reflective%20Cat%20Collar%20can%20display%20up%20to%2024%20letters%20and%20numbers.%20It%20has%20an%20adjustable%20length%2C%20breakaway%20buckle%2C%20reflective%20strip%2C%20and%20removable%20bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20cat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862bbdbf748d8c055f4a57b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrisco%20makes%20the%20most%20comfortable%20personalized%20cat%20collar%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECollars%20with%20your%20cat's%20info%20printed%20in%20ink%20can%20blur%20over%20time.%20Embroidered%20styles%20hold%20up%20better%2C%20but%20we%20noticed%20they%20often%20have%20a%20rough%20backing%20that%20may%20irritate%20your%20cat's%20skin%20or%20even%20cause%20hair%20loss.%20The%20Frisco%20collar%20uses%20laser%20etching%20instead.%20It's%20not%20perfect%20%E2%80%94the%20etching%20was%20a%20bit%20uneven%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20characters%20didn't%20fade%2C%20bleed%2C%20or%20scratch%20off%2C%20even%20after%20washing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217a2367d-05b1-4d58-8bd1-8ea6a61dacd3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cat%20collars%20aren't%20the%20priciest%20item%20on%20a%20new%20cat%20shopping%20list%2C%20but%20you%20may%20want%20to%20save%20a%20few%20bucks%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20unsure%20how%20your%20cat%20will%20react%20to%20wearing%20one.%20Red%20Dingo's%20Cat%20Collar%20doesn't%20come%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20patterns%20or%20feature%20fancy%20hardware.%20However%2C%20its%20no-frills%20design%20makes%20it%20affordable%20without%20skimping%20on%20safety%2C%20featuring%20a%20reliable%20breakaway%20clasp.%20This%20collar%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20color-coordinated%20bell%20that%20can%20be%20removed%20for%20noise-sensitive%20cats%20or%20feline%20caregivers.%5C%22%3ECat%20collars%20aren't%20the%20priciest%20item%20on%20a%20new%20cat%20shopping%20list%2C%20but%20you%20may%20want%20to%20save%20a%20few%20bucks%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20unsure%20how%20your%20cat%20will%20react%20to%20wearing%20one.%20Red%20Dingo's%20Cat%20Collar%20doesn't%20come%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20patterns%20or%20feature%20fancy%20hardware.%20However%2C%20its%20no-frills%20design%20makes%20it%20affordable%20without%20skimping%20on%20safety%2C%20featuring%20a%20reliable%20breakaway%20clasp.%20This%20collar%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20color-coordinated%20bell%20that%20can%20be%20removed%20for%20noise-sensitive%20cats%20or%20feline%20caregivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22red%20dingo%20collar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c3703d5881a51c1c5ecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20no-frills%20Red%20Dingo%20Cat%20Collar%20passed%20our%20breakaway%20test%20with%20flying%20colors.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERed%20Dingo's%20budget-friendly%20cat%20collar%20is%20made%20from%20durable%2C%20easy-to-clean%20nylon%20and%20dried%20the%20fastest%20in%20our%20soak%20test.%20That's%20important%20because%20a%20wet%20collar%20can%20be%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20bacteria%20and%20irritate%20your%20cat's%20skin%2C%20Cahn%20s