rotect%20against%20heartworm%20or%20intestinal%20parasites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22seresto%20collar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c45bf748d8c055f4a667%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Seresto%20Flea%20Collar%20comes%20recommended%20by%20veterinarians%20for%20its%20safety%20and%20effectiveness.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%2024%20hours%2C%20this%20non-greasy%2C%20odorless%2C%20and%20water-resistant%20collar%20starts%20killing%20fleas.%20It%20works%20by%20slowly%20releasing%20active%20ingredients%2C%20providing%20cats%20with%20continuous%20protection%20against%20adult%20fleas%2C%20flea%20larvae%2C%20and%20ticks%20for%20up%20to%20eight%20months.%20The%20collar%20is%20adjustable%2C%20which%20is%20important%20because%20it%20must%20contact%20the%20cat's%20skin%20to%20be%20effective.%20Elanco%20offers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzvk_-y9ScCo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20how-to%20video%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20sizing%20for%20comfort%20and%20efficacy.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20quick-release%20buckle.%20Talk%20to%20your%20vet%20before%20switching%20from%20a%20topical%20treatment%20to%20a%20flea%20collar%2C%20and%20always%20purchase%20these%20collars%20from%20reputable%20retailers%20such%20as%20Chewy%2C%20Petsmart%2C%20or%20Petco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc669bc5-dd7c-4209-90ae-e87b1ad863c6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20cat%20collar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20can%20be%20sensitive%20about%20what%20they%20wear%2C%20and%20as%20agile%20animals%20who%20squeeze%20through%20tight%20spaces%2C%20the%20wrong%20collar%20can%20be%20downright%20dangerous.%20Here%20are%20the%20qualities%20our%20experts%20recommend%20considering%20when%20searching%20for%20comfortable%20and%20safe%20collars%20for%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20breakaway%20clasp%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BA%20breakaway%20collar%20is%20vital%20for%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmypetsvet.co.uk%2Fpages%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Nick%20Horniman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BVSc%2C%20MRCVS%2C%20veterinary%20surgeon%20and%20founder%20of%20MyPetsVet.%20A%20breakaway%20clasp%20typically%20resembles%20a%20small%20plastic%20buckle%20with%20two%20interlocking%20prongs%20that%20snap%20together%20and%20pop%20open%20under%20pressure.%20%26quot%3BCats%20are%20natural%20climbers%20and%20explorers%2C%20so%20collars%20can%20easily%20get%20caught%20on%20branches%2C%20fences%2C%20or%20furniture.%20A%20non-breakaway%20collar%20can%20cause%20serious%20injury%20or%20even%20strangulation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisibility%20and%20auditory%20aids%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20best%20cat%20collars%20include%20safety%20features%20like%20reflective%20stitching%20or%20strips%20and%20removable%20bells.%20Reflective%20materials%20bounce%20light%20back%2C%20helping%20make%20your%20cat%20visible%20to%20cars%20or%20flashlights%20at%20night.%20Bells%20help%20protect%20wildlife%20by%20warning%20them%20that%20your%20cat%20is%20nearby.%20%26quot%3BA%20collar%20with%20a%20bell%20may%20also%20help%20prevent%20indoor%20cats%20from%20stalking%20people%20or%20other%20cats%20in%20the%20household%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%20are%20made%20from%20nylon%2C%20which%20is%20durable%2C%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20retain%20moisture%20or%20scents.%20These%20are%20important%20factors%20for%20cats%20who%20spend%20time%20outdoors.%20For%20indoor-only%20cats%2C%20collars%20can%20be%20made%20from%20various%20materials%20that%20go%20beyond%20typical%20nylon%20webbing%2C%20including%20soft%20velvet%2C%20patterned%20cotton%2C%20or%20canvas.%20These%20are%20the%20materials%20recommended%20by%20Ingrid%20Johnson%2C%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fundamentallyfeline.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFundamentally%20Feline%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20prefers%20these%20fabrics%20for%20cat%20collars%20because%20they%20are%20gentle%20on%20the%20skin%20and%20reduce%20friction.%20Horniman%20recommends%20avoiding%20materials%20that%20are%20rough%20or%20rigid%2C%20such%20as%20plastic-coated%20collars%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20irritation%20and%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20and%20width%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDangling%20charms%20and%20decorative%20studs%20may%20look%20cute%2C%20but%20they%20add%20extra%20weight%20to%20cat%20collars%2C%20making%20them%20uncomfortable%20to%20wear.%20Horniman%20says%20lightweight%20collars%20are%20best%2C%20particularly%20ones%20that%20weigh%20less%20than%20%E2%85%93%20ounce.%20Jangly%20charms%20may%20also%20frighten%20noise-sensitive%20cats%20or%20be%20irritating%20to%20cat%20parents.%20Collar%20width%20matters%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BNarrow%20collars%20are%20typically%20more%20comfortable%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they're%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20support%20an%20ID%20tag%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%20Most%20cat%20collars%20are%20about%20%C2%BD%20inch%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20length%20of%20a%20collar%20should%20be%20adjustable%20to%20fit%20your%20cat%20properly.%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20be%20able%20to%20comfortably%20fit%20two%20fingers%20between%20the%20collar%20and%20the%20cat's%20neck%2C%20and%20the%20collar%20should%20be%20able%20to%20rotate%20without%20much%20effort%2C%20but%20should%20not%20be%20so%20loose%20that%20it%20is%20dangling%2C%26quot%3B%20Dixon%20says.%20The%20best%20cat%20collars%20for%20kittens%20should%20adjust%20to%20as%20small%20as%206%20inches%20in%20neck%20circumference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277e998cf-0cca-4d2d-b97c-05e8e37ef612%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pawtitas%20fray%20test%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862cae83d5881a51c1c5fd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20making%20partial%20cuts%20in%20the%20collar%20materials%2C%20we%20added%20tension%20to%20see%20if%20they%20continued%20to%20fray.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%2017%20different%20cat%20collars%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20options%20for%20most%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreakaway%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20tested%20the%20strength%20of%20each%20breakaway%20buckle%20by%20looping%20the%20collars%20around%20a%20sturdy%20leg%20of%20a%20table%20or%20cat%20tree%20and%20applying%20steadily%20increasing%20pressure.%20We%20began%20with%20a%20gentle%20tug%20that%20incrementally%20increased%20in%20intensity%20every%20five%20seconds%20and%20noted%20at%20which%20point%20the%20buckle%20came%20apart.%20Collars%20that%20broke%20away%20with%20a%20medium%20amount%20of%20pressure%20were%20ranked%20higher%20as%20they%20would%20prevent%20accidental%20strangulation%2C%20but%20stay%20on%20in%20less%20sticky%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFray%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20made%20a%201-centimeter%20cut%20in%20the%20webbing%20of%20all%20but%20the%20calming%20and%20flea%20collars.%20Then%20we%20hung%20a%2015-ounce%20can%20of%20beans%20or%20a%205-pound%20weight%20from%20each%20collar.%20After%2024%20hours%2C%20we%20checked%20the%20nick%20for%20expansion%20or%20fraying.%20We%20rechecked%20the%20cut%20after%20the%20collars%20had%20gone%20through%20the%20clean%20test%20to%20identify%20any%20additional%20fraying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOdor%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20soaked%20the%20collars%20in%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20for%2010%20minutes%2C%20then%20rinsed%20them%20out%20in%20hot%20water%20and%20left%20them%20to%20dry%20overnight.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20scored%20the%20odor's%20strength%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201%20to%204%20by%20placing%20the%20collar%20on%20a%20table%20and%20sitting%203%20feet%20away%2C%20then%20gradually%20moving%20closer.%20We%20also%20rechecked%20the%20collars%20after%20the%20clean%20test%20and%20scored%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20remaining%20scent%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoak%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20expanded%20each%20of%20the%20collars%20in%20the%20breakaway%2C%20waterproof%2C%20reflective%2C%20personalized%2C%20and%20bow%20tie%20categories%20to%20their%20maximum%20length%20and%20measured%20them.%20Following%20the%20vinegar%20and%20odor%20tests%2C%20which%20included%20thorough%20soaking%20and%20overnight%20drying%2C%20we%20measured%20the%20collars%20again%20to%20check%20for%20shrinkage.%20We%20also%20noted%20how%20quickly%20the%20collars%20dried%20after%20they'd%20been%20soaked%20in%20water%2C%20checking%20them%20at%202%20hours%2C%204%20hours%2C%20and%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClean%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20rubbed%20each%20collar%20in%20soil%20and%20let%20them%20sit%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20washing%20and%20drying%20them%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions.%20Once%20dry%2C%20we%20examined%20each%20collar%20for%20dirt%20and%20discoloration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReflective%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20placed%20each%20reflective%20collar%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20and%20shined%20a%20flashlight%20on%20them%2C%20gradually%20stepping%20farther%20back%20from%20the%20collar%20(5%2C%2010%2C%20and%2015%20feet)%20to%20note%20visibility%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudibility%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20help%20from%20a%20partner%2C%20we%20jingled%20each%20collar%20with%20a%20bell%2C%20gradually%20stepping%20farther%20back%20(5%2C%2010%2C%20and%2015%20feet)%20to%20detect%20audibility.%20This%20test%20was%20completed%20both%20indoors%20and%20outdoors%20in%20an%20urban%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285dc3ee5-45c2-4c09-ad13-66cefd3ae969%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ECat%20collar%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20vets%20recommend%20collars%20for%20cats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20recommend%20breakaway%20collars%20as%20an%20added%20layer%20of%20protection%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.avma.org%2Fresources-tools%2Fpet-owners%2Fpetcare%2Fmicrochips-reunite-pets-families%2Fmicrochipping-faq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrochipping%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Cahn%20says%20collars%20can%20help%20people%20differentiate%20between%20owned%20versus%20community%20cats%2C%20protect%20wildlife%2C%20or%20provide%20parasite%20prevention.%20Collars%20with%20bells%20can%20also%20discourage%20stalking%20behavior%20toward%20people%20or%20other%20pets%20in%20the%20home.%20That%20said%2C%20collars%20come%20with%20the%20risk%20of%20injury%20or%20strangulation%20if%20they%20become%20caught.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20vet%2C%20my%20only%20stipulation%20is%20that%20if%20a%20pet%20owner%20decides%20to%20put%20a%20collar%20on%20their%20cat%2C%20it%20must%20be%20a%20breakaway%20collar%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20a%20cat%20collar%20with%20a%20bell%20good%20or%20bad%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDomestic%2C%20free-roaming%20cats%20are%20estimated%20to%20kill%20upwards%20of%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-10526-20%26h%3De63ca31278e825dfa9cdbf40b4f80480821aaa0317282f589de06b2963a5cdb6%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4142b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-collar%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fncomms2380%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4%20billion%20birds%20and%2022%20billion%20mammals%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20each%20year%2C%20making%20them%20the%20top%20human-related%20threat%20to%20US%20wildlife.%20Cats%20don't%20just%20hunt%20for%20food%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fmam.12230%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopportunistic%20hunters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20they%20hunt%20whether%20they%20are%20hungry%20or%20not.%20According%20to%20Cahn%2C%20collars%20with%20bells%20can%20help%20warn%20wildlife%20of%20a%20cat's%20presence%20and%20may%20discourage%20stalking%20behaviors%20in%20indoor%20cats.%20But%20for%20some%20cats%2C%20bells%20are%20annoying%20or%20scary%20and%20can%20make%20wearing%20a%20collar%20less%20tolerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20indoor%20cats%20need%20collars%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERenzullo%20and%20Johnson%20agree%20that%20indoor%20cats%20should%20wear%20a%20collar%20that%20clearly%20displays%20their%20ID.%20%26quot%3BCats%20get%20outside%2C%20windows%20get%20broken%2C%20people%20break%20into%20houses%2C%20stuff%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Johnson.%20%26quot%3BI've%20adopted%20the%20philosophy%20that%20they%20should%20all%20have%20a%20collar.%20It's%20their%20best%20chance%20of%20being%20ID'd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20fit%20my%20cat%20for%20a%20cat%20collar%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20properly%20fit%20your%20cat's%20collar%20to%20prevent%20injury%20or%20discomfort.%20Fadl%20says%20a%20correctly%20fitted%20collar%20should%20be%20just%20loose%20enough%20for%20you%20to%20be%20able%20to%20slide%20two%20fingers%20between%20it%20and%20your%20cat's%20neck.%20Check%20the%20collar%20shortly%20after%20you%20adjust%20it%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20the%20proper%20size.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20growing%20kitten%2C%20check%20the%20collar%20weekly%20to%20be%20sure%20it%20doesn't%20become%20too%20tight%20as%20they%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20a%20cat%20need%20a%20collar%20if%20they%20are%20microchipped%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20or%20not%20cats%20should%20wear%20collars%20is%20a%20surprisingly%20controversial%20topic%20and%20should%20be%20determined%20by%20pet%20owners%20based%20on%20their%20individual%20cat's%20lifestyle%20and%20temperament%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%20While%20collars%20do%20carry%20some%20risk%2C%20using%20one%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%20with%20your%20contact%20info%20can%20increase%20the%20chances%20your%20cat%20makes%20it%20home%20safely.%20If%20your%20cat%20gets%20lost%20or%20separated%20from%20you%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20they%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20facility%20with%20a%20microchip%20scanner%2C%20such%20as%20a%20veterinary%20practice%2C%20animal%20control%20facility%2C%20animal%20shelter%2C%20or%20some%20police%20and%20fire%20stations.%20If%20your%20cat's%20ID%20and%20phone%20number%20are%20clearly%20displayed%20on%20their%20collar%2C%20you'll%20have%20a%20much%20better%20chance%20of%20getting%20your%20cat%20back%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20kittens%20wear%20collars%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20microchipping%2C%20putting%20a%20collar%20on%20your%20kitten%20adds%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20protection%20if%20they%20slip%20out%20the%20door%20or%20get%20loose%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20vet.%20To%20prevent%20accidents%2C%20properly%20fit%20the%20collar%20so%20that%20it%20isn't%20too%20loose%20or%20too%20tight%20%E2%80%94%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20fit%20two%20fingers%20comfortably%20between%20the%20collar%20and%20your%20kitten's%20neck.%20Most%20collars%20for%20kittens%20adjust%20to%20as%20small%20as%20a%206-inch%20neck%20circumference.%20Kittens%20who%20have%20positive%20experiences%20with%20collars%20early%20on%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20comfortable%20wearing%20them%20as%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20should%20a%20cat%20wear%20a%20collar%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20can%20wear%20collars%20all%20the%20time%20as%20long%20as%20the%20collar%20fits%20properly%2C%20has%20a%20breakaway%20clasp%2C%20and%20isn't%20irritating%20to%20your%20cat.%20Horiman%20says%20soft%2C%20flexible%20materials%20reduce%20irritation%20and%20shouldn't%20cause%20hair%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%20are%20hardly%20noticeable%20to%20cats.%20Still%2C%20some%20pet%20parents%20prefer%20to%20use%20collars%20only%20when%20traveling%20or%20when%20escape%20risks%20are%20higher%2C%20like%20vet%20visits%20or%20when%20guests%20are%20coming%20and%20going.%20If%20your%20cat%20wears%20a%20GPS%20tracker%2C%20bow%20tie%2C%20or%20other%20accessories%2C%20they%20may%20be%20more%20comfortable%20with%20the%20collar%20removed%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20get%20my%20cat%20used%20to%20a%20collar%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20collar%20doesn't%20come%20naturally%20to%20most%20cats.%20For%20best%20results%20and%20to%20minimize%20stress%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20use%20baby%20steps%20and%20positive%20reinforcement-based%20training.%20Our%20experts%20recommend%20introducing%20the%20collar%20by%20letting%20your%20cat%20sniff%20and%20explore%20the%20collar%20before%20trying%20it%20on.%20When%20you%20see%20your%20cat%20investigating%20the%20collar%2C%20praise%20them%20and%20give%20them%20a%20treat.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20try%20spraying%20the%20collar%20with%20Feliway%20or%20rubbing%20it%20on%20their%20bedding%20or%20favorite%20toys%20to%20infuse%20it%20with%20familiar%20scents%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20says.%20Hold%20the%20collar%20near%20their%20fur%20while%20offering%20treats%20or%20gentle%20pets%20if%20your%20cat%20likes%20to%20be%20touched.%20Once%20your%20cat%20is%20comfortable%2C%20place%20the%20unclasped%20collar%20around%20their%20neck%20for%20short%20periods%2C%20paired%20with%20praise%2C%20treats%2C%20or%20play.%20Then%20try%20briefly%20clasping%20the%20collar%20and%20over%20multiple%20short%20training%20sessions%2C%20gradually%20increasing%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20they%20wear%20it.%20Watch%20for%20signs%20of%20discomfort%20or%20stress%2C%20such%20as%20excessive%20scratching%20or%20attempts%20to%20remove%20the%20collar.%20Remember%2C%20not%20every%20cat%20will%20accept%20a%20collar%2C%20so%20we%20recommend%20working%20with%20a%20positive%20reinforcement-based%20trainer%20if%20you%20deem%20it%20essential%20for%20your%20cat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Rogz%20Night%20Cat%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20green%20Rogz%20Nightcat%20cat%20collar%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7b56cbee0fc0019d5ae16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Rogz%20collar%20has%20all%20the%20qualities%20we%20look%20for%20in%20a%20great%20cat%20collar.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Orange%2C%20lime%2C%20yellow%2C%20purple%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E8%26quot%3B%20to%2012%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%203%2F8%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20unique%20breakaway%20buckle%20that%20can%20be%20adjusted%20to%20come%20apart%20with%20light%2C%20medium%2C%20or%20heavy%20pressure%2C%20the%20Rogz%20Night%20Cat%20Reflective%20Collar%20is%20ideal%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20sizes%20and%20activity%20levels.%20That%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20highly%20reflective%20exterior%20that's%20easily%20visible%20in%20low%20light%20and%20an%20adjustable%20length%2C%20makes%20the%20Rogz%20collar%20the%20most%20versatile%20of%20those%20we%20considered.%20In%20our%20testing%2C%20the%20Rogz%20Nightcat%20proved%20durable%20and%20easy%20to%20clean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20our%20experts%20agree%20that%20a%20collar%20with%20a%20buckle%20that%20comes%20apart%20when%20force%20is%20applied%2C%20known%20as%20a%20breakaway%20collar%2C%20is%20the%20only%20type%20of%20collar%20a%20cat%20should%20wear.%20%26quot%3BThe%20breakaway%20collars%20are%20really%20the%20safest%20for%20the%20animal%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethosvet.com%2Fteam-member%2Flindsay-renzullo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Lindsey%20Renzullo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20medical%20director%20at%20Ethos%20Veterinary%20Health.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20they%20get%20stuck%20on%20something%2C%20if%20they%20pull%20hard%20enough%2C%20they%20are%20able%20to%20get%20it%20off.%26quot%3B%20The%20ideal%20breakaway%20collar%20comes%20apart%20in%20dangerous%20situations%20but%20otherwise%20stays%20buckled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Red%20Dingo%20Classic%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20light%20blue%20red%20dingo%20nylon%20cat%20collar%20with%20bell%20and%20fish-shaped%20clasp%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20tabletop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bc325506706e0019a97559%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20affordable%20Red%20Dingo%20Classic%20Collar%20comes%20in%20multiple%20colors%20with%20matching%20bells.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Black%2C%20blue%2C%20green%2C%20purple%2C%20red%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E8%26quot%3B%20to%2012.5%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%201%2F2%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%2C%20a%20classic%2C%20no-frills%20design%20is%20always%20a%20good%20bet.%20Classic%20collars%20are%20typically%20made%20from%20nylon%20or%20similar%20easy-to-clean%20fabric%20and%20have%20a%20breakaway%20buckle.%20It's%20this%20simple%20design%20that%20makes%20them%20so%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERed%20Dingo's%20Classic%20Cat%20Collar%20proved%20strong%20and%20versatile%20in%20our%20testing.%20It%20frayed%20very%20little%20when%20we%20made%20a%20small%20cut%20in%20the%20nylon%2C%20and%20the%20cute%2C%20fish-shaped%20buckle%20broke%20apart%20with%20the%20ideal%20amount%20of%20pressure.%20Two%20washings%20removed%20all%20lingering%20odors%20of%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20and%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20waterproof%20collars%20we%20evaluated%2C%20Red%20Dingo's%20was%20the%20fastest%20to%20dry%20after%20soaking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20waterproof%3A%20Ruff%20Threads%20Biothane%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20Ruff%20Threads%20Biothane%20cat%20collar%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7b86c02ac410018f93e15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20waterproof%20Ruff%20Threads%20collar%20is%20sized%20specifically%20for%20your%20cat.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2030%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECustom%2C%203%2F8%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOptional%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20both%20of%20the%20waterproof%20collars%20we%20considered%20were%20good%2C%20we%20like%20the%20Ruff%20Threads%20Biothane%20Cat%20Collar%20for%20its%20ultra-simple%20design%20and%20durable%20material.%20Renzullo%20likes%20waterproof%20collars%20because%20they%20won't%20become%20a%20soggy%2C%20moist%20burden%20around%20your%20cat's%20neck%20if%20they%20get%20wet.%20Unlike%20most%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%2C%20which%20are%20made%20from%20nylon%20or%20polyester%20fabric%2C%20waterproof%20collars%20are%20made%20from%20Biothane%20or%20a%20similar%20smooth%2C%20coated%20material.%20Cats%20who%20are%20sensitive%20to%20wearing%20a%20collar%20may%20find%20this%20material%20more%20comfortable%20because%20it's%20less%20likely%20to%20get%20caught%20in%20long%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20testing%20confirmed%20that%20this%20isn't%20just%20the%20fastest-drying%20collar%2C%20but%20it%20also%20excels%20at%20repelling%20odors.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20only%20collar%20in%20the%20guide%20that%20is%20custom-sized.%20Instead%20of%20adjusting%20the%20length%20to%20fit%20your%20cat%2C%20you%20send%20Ruff%20Threads%20either%20your%20kitty's%20neck%20size%20or%20collar%20length%2C%20and%20they%20customize%20it.%20The%20collar%20has%20a%20breakaway%20buckle%20and%20comes%20in%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20glow-in-the-dark%3A%20Pawtitas%20Glow%20in%20the%20Dark%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Pawtitas%20Glow%20in%20the%20Dark%20cat%20collar%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7ba53bee0fc0019d5ae24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20glow-in-the-dark%20collars%20are%20practical%20and%20cute.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2015%20colors%20with%20prints%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E8%26quot%3B%20to%2012%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%203%2F8%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dark%2C%20cats%20are%20nearly%20invisible%20to%20drivers.%20A%20reflective%20collar%20gives%20them%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20being%20seen.%20Even%20better%20is%20a%20collar%20that%20glows%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20so%20it's%20visible%20even%20if%20headlights%20aren't%20shining%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pawtitas%20Glow%20in%20the%20Dark%20Cat%20Collar%20was%20the%20brightest%20we%20tested.%20It%20gets%20its%20vivid%20glow%20from%20a%20ribbon%20of%20patterned%20material%20sewn%20onto%20ripstop%20nylon%20webbing.%20The%20Pawtitas%20collar%20held%20up%20extremely%20well%20in%20our%20fray%2C%20soak%2C%20and%20clean%20tests.%20It%20also%20has%20an%20adjustable%20length%20and%20breakaway%20buckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20personalized%3A%20GoTags%20Personalized%20Embroidered%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20Go%20Tags%20Personalized%20Breakaway%20Collar%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7bf76bee0fc0019d5ae5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20GoTags%20collar%20meets%20our%20criteria%20for%20a%20great%20personalized%20collar%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20embroidered%20characters.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205%20colors%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E8%26quot%3B%20to%2012%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%201%2F2%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EID%20tags%20can%20fall%20off%2C%20but%20a%20personalized%20collar%20with%20your%20contact%20information%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20stay%20put.%20The%20GoTags%20Collar%20is%20made%20of%20durable%20nylon%20and%20can%20be%20embroidered%20with%20up%20to%2021%20letters%20and%20numbers.%20You%20can%20choose%20from%2014%20colors%20of%20embroidery%20thread.%20The%20collar%20performed%20well%20in%20testing%2C%20with%20minimal%20fraying%20and%20only%20mild%20lingering%20odors%20after%20soaking%20in%20vinegar.%20It%20has%20an%20adjustable%20length%20and%20breakaway%20buckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20kitty%20ever%20gets%20lost%2C%20having%20as%20many%20forms%20of%20identification%20as%20possible%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20may%20help%20them%20be%20returned%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbondvet.com%2Fcareers%2Fmeet-the-team%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gabrielle%20Fadl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20medical%20director%20at%20Bond%20Vet.%20Plus%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20cat%20who%20is%20sensitive%20to%20wearing%20things%20around%20its%20neck%2C%20a%20personalized%20collar%20may%20be%20more%20comfortable%20for%20them%20than%20dangling%2C%20jingling%20tags.%20Skip%20personalized%20collars%20with%20your%20cat's%20info%20printed%20in%20ink%20because%20it%20can%20easily%20become%20blurred%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20bow%20tie%3A%20Made%20by%20Cleo%20Bow%20Tie%20Collar%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20Made%20by%20Cleo%20Rifle%20Paper%20Co%20Bowtie%20cat%20collar%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7cda402ac410018f93e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMade%20by%20Cleo%20is%20our%20go-to%20brand%20for%20adorable%20bow%20tie%20collars.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20200%2B%20patterns%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E3%20sizes%20from%206%26quot%3B%20to%2016%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%201%2F2%26quot%3B%20wide%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fashionable%20collar%20is%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20showcase%20your%20cat's%20personality.%20Collars%20can%20be%20made%20from%20various%20materials%20that%20go%20beyond%20typical%20nylon%20webbing%2C%20including%20soft%20velvet%2C%20patterned%20cotton%2C%20or%20canvas%20fabric.%20These%20are%20the%20materials%20Ingrid%20Johnson%2C%20a%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fundamentallyfeline.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFundamentally%20Feline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gravitates%20toward.%20Bits%20and%20bobbles%20like%20bow%20ties%20and%20charms%20also%20make%20lovely%20accents%20without%20being%20overly%20burdensome%20for%20most%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoosing%20our%20favorite%20bow%20tie%20collar%20was%20the%20hardest%20decision%20we%20had%20to%20make%20for%20this%20guide.%20Both%20options%20performed%20similarly%20in%20testing%20and%20were%20super%20cute%20on%20our%20feline%20models.%20Ultimately%2C%20we%20went%20with%20Made%20by%20Cleo's%20Bow%20Tie%20Collar%20Set.%20This%20adjustable%20collar%20has%20a%20patterned%20fabric%20exterior%20and%20a%20webbed%20nylon%20interior%2C%20which%20proved%20highly%20durable%20in%20our%20fray%2C%20odor%2C%20and%20clean%20tests.%20After%20being%20washed%20twice%2C%20the%20fabric%20was%20slightly%20discolored%2C%20but%20the%20collar%20held%20up%20well%20otherwise.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20the%203-inch-wide%20bow%20tie%2C%20about%2030%25%20larger%20than%20the%20Neocoichi%20collar%20bow%20tie%2C%20was%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20our%2010-%20and%2012-pound%20cats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fleas%3A%20Seresto%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Collar%20for%20Cats%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20round%20open%20metal%20tin%20with%20text%20Seresto%20Flea%20Collar%20for%20cats%20is%20open%20to%20reveal%20a%20cat%20flea%20collar%20inside%20on%20a%20blue%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fb415e0402d49001924f58e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVets%20recommend%20the%20Seresto%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Collar%20above%20all%20other%20options.%3Cp%3ESeresto%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Only%20one%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUp%20to%2016%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%2C%20trim%20to%20fit%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20considerations%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20for%20use%20in%20kittens%20under%2010%20weeks%20old%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EFlea%20collars%20are%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-flea-prevention-cats%5C%22%3Ebest%20flea%20treatments%20for%20cats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Of%20the%20flea%20collars%20on%20the%20market%2C%20Renzullo%20likes%20the%20Seresto%20Flea%20and%20Tick%20Collar%20for%20Cats.%20%26quot%3BSeresto%20is%20really%20good%20and%20efficacious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20This%20non-greasy%2C%20odorless%2C%20and%20water-resistant%20collar%20repels%20and%20kills%20fleas%20and%20ticks%20and%20keeps%20them%20at%20bay%20for%20up%20to%20eight%20months.%20The%20collar%20is%20adjustable%20and%20has%20a%20quick-release%20buckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFadl%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20buy%20a%20flea%20collar%20specifically%20designed%20for%20felines.%20You%20should%20also%20talk%20to%20your%20vet%20before%20switching%20from%20a%20topical%20treatment%20to%20a%20flea%20collar.%20Always%20purchase%20these%20collars%20from%20reputable%20online%20retailers%20like%20Chewy%20or%20Petco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20calming%3A%20Comfort%20Zone%20On-the-Go%20Calming%20Collar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Comfort%20Zone%20Pheromone%20cat%20collar%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7d24c02ac410018f93e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20best%20calming%20cat%20collar%20has%20a%20breakaway%20feature%20for%20added%20safety.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColors%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Only%20one%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUp%2016%26quot%3B%20neck%20circumference%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemovable%20bell%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20considerations%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20for%20use%20in%20kittens%20under%2010%20months%20old%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3ECalming%20pheromones%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20reduce%20stress%20and%20unwanted%20behaviors%20in%20both%20cats%20and%20dogs.%20Calming%20collars%20made%20for%20felines%20are%20infused%20with%20a%20synthetic%20version%20of%20the%20pheromone%20a%20mother%20cat%20emits%20while%20nursing%20her%20babies.%20The%20collar%20steadily%20releases%20its%20calming%20power%20each%20time%20it%20rubs%20against%20a%20cat's%20fur%20and%20typically%20lasts%2030%20days%20before%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recommend%20the%20Comfort%20Zone%20On-the-Go%20Calming%20Cat%20Collar.%20Daintier%20and%20easier%20to%20adjust%20than%20Sentry's%20HC%20Good%20Behavior%20Pheromone%20Collar%2C%20this%20collar%20is%20secured%20much%20like%20a%20watch%20band%2C%20which%20prevents%20it%20from%20flopping%20around%20or%20sticking%20out.%20In%20an%20emergency%2C%20pressure%20on%20the%20collar%20causes%20the%20ridges%20to%20break%20free%20from%20their%20holes%20and%20the%20buckle%20to%20come%20undone.%20The%20On-the-Go%20Calming%20Collar%20is%20unscented%20and%20lasts%20for%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20cat%20collars%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20cat%20collars%20being%20tested%20by%20holding%20cans%20from%20the%20back%20of%20a%20chair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7d2f6bee0fc0019d5aed2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20best%20cat%20collars%20passed%20a%20series%20of%20durability%20tests.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%2013%20different%20cat%20collars%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20options%20for%20most%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreakaway%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20tested%20the%20strength%20of%20each%20breakaway%20buckle%20by%20looping%20the%20collars%20around%20a%20sturdy%20table%20leg%20and%20applying%20steadily%20increasing%20pressure.%20We%20began%20with%20a%20gentle%20tug%20that%20incrementally%20increased%20in%20intensity%20every%20five%20seconds%20and%20noted%20at%20which%20point%20the%20buckle%20came%20apart.%20Collars%20that%20broke%20away%20with%20a%20medium%20amount%20of%20pressure%20were%20ranked%20higher%20as%20they%20would%20prevent%20accidental%20strangulation%20but%20stay%20on%20in%20less%20sticky%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFray%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20made%20a%201-centimeter%20cut%20in%20the%20webbing%20of%20all%20but%20the%20calming%20and%20flea%20collars.%20Then%20we%20hung%20a%2015-ounce%20can%20of%20beans%20from%20each%20collar%20and%20left%20it%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20checking%20to%20see%20if%20the%20weight%20caused%20the%20nick%20in%20the%20collar%20to%20expand%20or%20fray.%20We%20rechecked%20the%20cut%20after%20the%20collars%20had%20gone%20through%20the%20clean%20test%20to%20identify%20any%20additional%20fraying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOdor%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20soaked%20the%20same%20collars%20subjected%20to%20the%20fray%20test%20in%20apple%20cider%20vinegar%20for%2010%20minutes%2C%20then%20rinsed%20them%20out%20in%20hot%20water%20and%20left%20them%20to%20dry%20overnight.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20scored%20the%20odor's%20strength%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201%20to%204.%20We%20rechecked%20the%20collars%20after%20the%20clean%20test%20and%20scored%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20remaining%20scent%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoak%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20expanded%20each%20of%20the%20collars%20in%20the%20breakaway%2C%20waterproof%2C%20reflective%2C%20personalized%2C%20and%20bow%20tie%20categories%20to%20their%20maximum%20length%20and%20measured%20them.%20Following%20the%20vinegar%20and%20odor%20tests%2C%20which%20included%20thorough%20soaking%20and%20overnight%20drying%2C%20we%20measured%20the%20collars%20again%20to%20check%20for%20shrinkage.%20We%20also%20noted%20how%20quickly%20each%20collar%20dried%2C%20checking%20them%20two%20hours%2C%20four%20hours%2C%20and%2012%20hours%20after%20they'd%20been%20soaked%20in%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClean%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20buried%20the%20same%20collars%20from%20the%20soak%20test%20in%20a%20bag%20of%20potting%20soil.%20After%2048%20hours%2C%20we%20washed%20them%20using%20hot%20water%20and%20dish%20soap%2C%20then%20laid%20them%20out%20to%20dry.%20Once%20dry%2C%20we%20examined%20each%20collar%20for%20dirt%20and%20discoloration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlow%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20completely%20dark%20room%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20the%20two%20glow-in-the-dark%20collars%20from%20three%20different%20distances%20(2%2C%205%2C%20and%2010%20feet%20away).%20At%20each%20distance%2C%20we%20noted%20how%20brightly%20the%20collars%20glowed%20compared%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECat%20collar%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tan%20brown%20and%20white%20colored%20cat%20wearing%20a%20green%20Ruff%20Threads%20BioThane%20Collar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b7dbb402ac410018f93ed9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20cats%20wore%20each%20of%20the%20contenders%20for%20the%20best%20cat%20collars.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20breakaway%20collars%20better%20for%20cats%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20Breakaway%20collars%20are%20built%20to%20prevent%20accidental%20strangulation.%20Whether%20a%20cat%20is%20indoors%20or%20outdoors%2C%20a%20collar%20can%20get%20stuck%20or%20tangled%20on%20things%20and%20push%20against%20the%20cat's%20windpipe.%20With%20a%20breakaway%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20your%20pet%20begins%20to%20struggle%2C%20the%20pressure%20opens%20the%20buckle%20to%20free%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20indoor%20cats%20need%20collars%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERenzullo%20and%20Johnson%20agree%20that%20indoor%20cats%20should%20wear%20a%20collar%20that%20clearly%20displays%20their%20ID.%20%26quot%3BCats%20get%20outside%2C%20windows%20get%20broken%2C%20people%20break%20into%20houses%2C%20stuff%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Johnson.%20%26quot%3BI've%20adopted%20the%20philosophy%20that%20they%20should%20all%20have%20a%20collar.%20It's%20their%20best%20chance%20of%20being%20ID'd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20stop%20my%20cat%20from%20losing%20his%20collar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20not%20much%20you%20can%20do%20to%20prevent%20your%20cat%20from%20losing%20its%20collar.%20In%20fact%2C%20if%20your%20cat%20loses%20their%20collar%2C%20it's%20probably%20a%20good%20sign%3B%20it%20means%20that%20they%20were%20able%20to%20escape%20after%20getting%20caught%20on%20something.%20To%20minimize%20lost%20collars%2C%20get%20one%20that%20won't%20break%20away%20with%20light%20pressure%20and%20one%20made%20of%20smooth%2C%20comfortable%20material%20like%20Biothane%2C%20which%20a%20cat%20will%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20scratch%20at.%20Be%20sure%20to%20fit%20it%20properly%2C%20leaving%20space%20for%20just%20two%20fingers%20between%20your%20cat's%20neck%20and%20the%20strap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20fit%20a%20cat%20collar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20properly%20fit%20your%20cat's%20collar%20to%20prevent%20injury%20or%20discomfort.%20For%20a%20cat%20collar%20to%20fit%20correctly%2C%20it%20should%20be%20just%20loose%20enough%20for%20you%20to%20be%20able%20to%20slide%20one%20or%20two%20fingers%20between%20it%20and%20your%20cat's%20neck%2C%20said%20Fadl.%20Check%20the%20collar%20shortly%20after%20you%20adjust%20it%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20the%20proper%20size.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20growing%20kitten%2C%20check%20the%20collar%20weekly%20to%20be%20sure%20it%20doesn't%20choke%20them%20as%20they%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20a%20cat%20need%20a%20collar%20if%20they%20are%20microchipped%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20If%20your%20cat%20gets%20lost%20or%20separated%20from%20you%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20the%20person%20who%20finds%20them%20can%20scan%20your%20cat's%20microchip%20without%20taking%20them%20to%20a%20veterinarian's%20office%20or%20animal%20shelter.%20If%20your%20cat's%20ID%20and%20phone%20number%20are%20clearly%20displayed%20on%20its%20collar%2C%20you%20have%20a%20much%20better%20chance%20of%20getting%20your%20pet%20back%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20kittens%20wear%20collars%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20The%20earlier%20a%20cat%20is%20introduced%20to%20wearing%20a%20collar%2C%20the%20better.%20A%20kitten%20who%20has%20positive%20experiences%20with%20collars%20early%20on%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20comfortable%20in%20a%20collar%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20I%20take%20off%20my%20cat's%20collar%20at%20night%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERemoving%20a%20cat's%20collar%20at%20night%20is%20unnecessary%20unless%20they%20are%20irritated%20by%20it.%20Most%20cats%20won't%20even%20notice%20it's%20on.%20If%20you%20have%20attached%20a%20bulky%20GPS%20tracker%20to%20their%20collar%2C%20they%20may%20be%20more%20comfortable%20if%20it%20is%20removed%20at%20night.%20Attaching%20a%20GPS%20tracker%20to%20a%20second%20collar%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20and%20take%20off%20without%20removing%20your%20pet's%20ID%20on%20their%20regular%20collar%20may%20be%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi