ht%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20set%20up%20the%20EcoFlow%20Wave%203%20in%20my%20window%2C%20I%20had%20to%20get%20crafty%20with%20some%20duct%20tape%20and%20an%20old%20portable%20air%20conditioner%20slider.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%2C%20though%2C%20that%20the%20Wave%203%20is%20designed%20for%20use%20away%20from%20home.%20EcoFlow%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151099065960r-20%26h%3Dd775f0435652f31732dbe903e6c301e0ecf3a062faa625703ed88aa0bdb0b253%26postID%3D6862950b3d1ce42a6af39656%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fecoflow-wave-3-air-conditioner-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fus.ecoflow.com%252Fproducts%252Fwave-series-car-vent-seal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecar%20vent%20seal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20use%20with%20RVs%20and%20other%20vehicles.%20Or%2C%20you%20can%20just%20close%20your%20vehicle's%20window%2C%20allowing%20just%20enough%20room%20for%20the%20hoses.%20Then%2C%20fill%20the%20gaps%20with%20what%20you%20have%20available%2C%20like%20clothing%2C%20tape%2C%20or%20whatever.%20Installing%20it%20in%20a%20tent%20is%20even%20easier%3A%20You%20just%20zip%20the%20door%20closed%20so%20the%20hoses%20can%20stick%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20steps%20included%20attaching%20the%20hoses%20to%20the%20unit%20using%20the%20provided%20exhaust%20duct%20adapter%20covers.%20Other%20than%20the%20duct%20tape%2C%20I%20didn't%20need%20any%20special%20tools%2C%20though%20I%20did%20need%20the%20directions%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20vents%20needed%20to%20be%20covered%2C%20since%20the%20configurations%20are%20different%20depending%20on%20whether%20you%20keep%20the%20Wave%203%20inside%20or%20outside%20the%20room%20you're%20cooling.%20If%20your%20situation%20allows%20for%20it%2C%20I%20recommend%20keeping%20the%20unit%20outside%20for%20better%20efficiency.%20My%20setup%20didn't%20allow%20it%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20to%20test%20that%20configuration%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221aa457af-164c-4b6c-b9f0-45bb8b0c3bb5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EPerformance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20all%20portable%20air%20conditioners%20through%20the%20same%20tests%2C%20including%20cooling%20a%20550-square-foot%20room.%20I%20compared%20temperatures%20before%20and%20after%20running%20them%20for%20two%20hours%20to%20assess%20their%20cooling%20performance.%20The%20EcoFlow%20Wave%203%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20by%20about%201.2%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20in%20the%20two%20hours%2C%20which%20isn't%20awful%20but%20also%20not%20particularly%20impressive%2C%20considering%20our%20top%20portable%20AC%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fmidea-portable-air-conditioner-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMidea%20Duo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20decreased%20the%20temperature%20by%203.3%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Wave%203%20is%20designed%20to%20cool%20areas%20up%20to%20180%20square%20feet%2C%20much%20smaller%20than%20our%20test%20room.%20So%2C%20I%20retested%20it%20in%20my%20200-square-foot%20bedroom%2C%20which%20is%20comparable%20to%20a%20small%20motorhome%20but%20larger%20than%20a%20typical%20tent%20or%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20relying%20on%20the%20wall%20outlet%2C%20the%20Wave%203%20cooled%20the%20smaller%20room%20by%203.2%20degrees%2C%20which%20is%20very%20good%20and%20an%20improvement%20on%20the%20Wave%202%2C%20which%20only%20cooled%20my%20room%20by%202%20degrees.%20Also%20impressive%20is%20how%20little%20power%20the%20Wave%203%20used.%20During%20the%20two-hour%20test%2C%20it%20only%20used%201%20kWh%20of%20energy%2C%20which%20is%20much%20better%20than%20any%20other%20portable%20AC%20I've%20tested%20and%20comparable%20to%20window%20ACs%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20be%20much%20more%20efficient.%20For%20context%2C%20if%20you%20were%20to%20run%20this%20unit%20on%20high%20for%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20every%20day%20during%20the%20summer%2C%20the%20power%20would%20cost%20you%20about%20%2459%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Felectricity%2Fmonthly%2Fepm_table_grapher.php%3Ft%3Depmt_5_6_a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20electricity%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Not%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20was%20a%20little%20better%20when%20using%20battery%20power.%20It%20cooled%20the%20smaller%20room%20by%203.6%20degrees.%20However%2C%20the%20battery%20only%20lasted%20two%20hours%20with%20the%20AC%20on%20full%20blast%2C%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%208%20hours%20Eco%20Flow%20claims%20in%20its%20marketing%20materials.%20For%20longer%20use%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20turn%20the%20AC%20down%20to%20low%2C%20buy%20extra%20batteries%2C%20or%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-portable-generator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerator%20or%20power%20station%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20battery%20charges%20via%20the%20wall%20outlet%20in%20under%2090%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20keep%20an%20air%20quality%20monitor%20in%20the%20testing%20room%20to%20see%20if%20there%20are%20any%20irregularities%20that%20you%20may%20need%20to%20know%20about.%20What%20struck%20me%20was%20how%20much%20better%20the%20room's%20air%20quality%20was%20after%20the%20testing%20period.%20The%20Wave%203%20appears%20to%20clean%20the%20air%20while%20it%20cools%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22581dfb3e-e5f8-4f5c-b1d5-4f6e31ed8ee1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Noise%5C%22%3ENoise%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wave%203%20is%20the%20quietest%20portable%20air%20conditioner%20I've%20tested.%20As%20measured%20with%20a%20decibel%20meter%20six%20feet%20away%2C%20the%20unit%20was%2042%20decibels%2C%20just%20a%20little%20louder%20than%20ambient%20sound.%20On%20high%2C%20it%20registered%2052%20decibels%2C%20which%20is%20quieter%20than%20a%20normal%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20hand%20holding%20a%20decibel%20meter%20in%20front%20of%20the%20ecoflow%20wave%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862cdd83d5881a51c1c601d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20a%20decibel%20meter%20to%20measure%20the%20sound%20output%20of%20the%20EcoFlow%20Wave%203%20from%20six%20feet%20away.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStreet%20racing%20is%20a%20popular%20pastime%20at%202%20a.m.%20outside%20my%20bedroom%20window%3A%20the%20louder%20the%20better%2C%20it%20seems.%20There%20were%20times%20I%20almost%20wished%20the%20AC%20was%20a%20little%20louder%20to%20drown%20out%20the%20noise.%20Still%2C%20though%2C%20if%20you%20take%20this%20unit%20camping%2C%20it%20won't%20drown%20out%20the%20serenity%20of%20nature%2C%20or%20the%20people%20partying%20at%20the%20site%20next%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2297a8d8e8-f553-40de-80a6-7a396fb2295a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20features%5C%22%3ESmart%20features%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20smart%20appliance%20must%20be%20user-friendly%20and%20reliable%2C%20and%20I%20much%20prefer%20an%20air%20conditioner%20with%20just%20a%20few%20features%20that%20operate%20reliably%20over%20a%20feature-rich%20unit%20that's%20unreliable.%20Once%20I%20connected%20the%20Wave%203%20to%20the%20EcoFlow%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fecoflow-power-a-new-world%2Fid1506693140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.ecoflow%26hl%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20which%20took%20about%20five%20minutes%2C%20the%20features%20worked%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20screenshots%20on%20the%20ecoflow%20wave%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862d0133d5881a51c1c6055%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20EcoFlow%20app%20is%20way%20more%20robust%20than%20the%20AC's%20onboard%20controls%2C%20and%20offers%20some%20unique%20settings%20like%20automatic%20drainage%20and%20a%20pet%20care%20mode.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20app%20more%20user-friendly%20than%20the%20on-unit%20buttons.%20On%20the%20main%20screen%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20the%20modes%3A%20Cool%2C%20Heat%2C%20Fan%2C%20Dry%2C%20and%20Auto.%20You%20can%20also%20adjust%20the%20intensity%20and%20the%20thermostat%20to%20achieve%20the%20precise%20temperature%20you%20want.%20The%20main%20screen%20also%20tells%20you%20how%20much%20wattage%20the%20unit%20is%20using%2C%20how%20much%20battery%20is%20left%2C%20and%20if%20you%20need%20to%20drain%20any%20water%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20innovative%20feature%20I%20haven't%20seen%20with%20other%20portable%20AC%20apps%20is%20Pet%20Care%20mode%2C%20which%20automatically%20turns%20on%20the%20Wave%203%20if%20the%20ambient%20temperature%20is%20above%2077%20degrees.%20You%20can%20also%20set%20limits%20on%20how%20much%20the%20battery%20charges%20or%20discharges%20to%20extend%20its%20life%20or%20save%20juice%20for%20an%20emergency.%20The%20scheduler%20and%20shut-off%20timer%20are%20also%20great%20energy-saving%20features%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5564675-cf6c-4527-8b07-267ffa4bb920%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Care%20and%20maintenance%5C%22%3ECare%20and%20maintenance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EcoFlow%20Wave%203%20is%20as%20easy%20to%20clean%20as%20other%20portable%20air%20conditioners.%20The%20most%20important%20task%20is%20cleaning%20the%20air%20inlet%20filters%20on%20the%20front%20and%20back%20of%20the%20appliance.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20you%20just%20press%20the%20tab%20on%20the%20bottom%20to%20release%20it%20and%20use%20a%20damp%20cloth%20to%20wipe%20away%20dust%20and%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20portable%20ACs%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20evaporate%20accumulated%20condensation%20and%20may%20only%20need%20to%20be%20emptied%20occasionally%20(if%20ever)%2C%20the%20EcoFlow%20Wave%203%20does%20not%20have%20such%20technology%20and%20will%20need%20to%20be%20emptied%20regularly.%20When%20the%20app%20notifies%20you%20that%20the%20water%20tank%20is%20full%2C%20you%20attach%20the%20drain%20pipe%20and%20press%20the%20drainage%20button%20to%20drain%20the%20water.%20If%20you%20live%20in%20a%20particularly%20humid%20area%2C%20you%20may%20have%20to%20do%20this%20every%20couple%20of%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2297653ade-9484-49d2-a13b-852b29b4e923%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20unimpressed%20with%20the%20Wave%203's%20heating%20performance%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20like%20that%20you%20still%20need%20to%20use%20the%20hoses%20to%20get%20the%20heat%20flowing.%20I%20tested%20it%20in%20the%20same%20200-square-foot%20room%20I%20used%20for%20the%20air%20conditioning%20test.%20In%20two%20hours%2C%20it%20only%20heated%20the%20room%20about%203.5%20degrees%2C%20and%20that%20used%20up%20all%20of%20the%20battery.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20average%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-space-heater%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20space%20heater%3C%2Fa%3E%20testing%20is%20an%208-degree%20increase%20in%20two%20hours.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20the%20space%20heaters%20we%20tested%20are%20battery-powered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20useful%20when%20staying%20at%20a%20drive-up%20campsite%2C%20the%20Wave%203%20may%20be%20impractical%20for%20camping%20off%20the%20beaten%20path%20due%20to%20its%2060-pound%20weight%20(when%20the%20unit%20and%20battery%20are%20paired%20together).%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20you%20really%20need%20your%20everyday%20comforts%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20stay%20closer%20to%20civilization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20Wave%203%20came%20with%20a%20window%20slider.%20I%20get%20that%20due%20to%20its%20variety%20of%20use%20cases%2C%20many%20users%20may%20never%20install%20it%20in%20a%20window.%20So%2C%20rather%20than%20providing%20a%20length%20of%20plastic%20that%20could%20end%20up%20in%20a%20landfill%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmanuals.ecoflow.com%2Fus%2Fproduct%2Fwave-3%3Flang%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEcoFlow%20gives%20tips%20for%20making%20your%20own%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20I%20don't%20like%20having%20to%20rely%20on%20duct%20tape%20and%20my%20craftiness.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20process%20is%20much%20simpler%20when%20using%20the%20unit%20in%20a%20vehicle%20or%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20this%20thing%20is%20expensive.%20You%20should%20really%20only%20consider%20it%20if%20a%20traditional%20window%20or%20portable%20AC%20won't%20work%20for%20your%20situation.%20Boats%2C%20RVs%2C%20and%20camping%20seem%20like%20the%20most%20typical%20uses%2C%20but%20again%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20devote%20precious%20space%20and%20weight%20to%20a%20very%20large%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234954d3a-f0a6-400a-8374-13844dddfa33%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerobreeze.com%2Fproducts%2Fzero-breeze-mark-3-ac%3Fvariant%3D41908672790630%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZero%20Breeze%20Mark%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20closest%20competitor%20to%20the%20Wave%203.%20Both%20the%20unit%20(22%20pounds)%20and%20the%20battery%20(14%20pounds)%20weigh%20less%20than%20the%20Wave%203%20and%20its%20battery.%20However%2C%20it%20doesn't%20put%20out%20as%20many%20Btu%20(5%2C280%20for%20the%20Mark%203%20versus%206%2C100