nsUnion%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThat%20number%20is%20either%20high%20because%20people%20cannot%20afford%20to%20pay%20their%20student%20loans%2C%20or%20don't%20think%20they%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20their%20student%20loans%2C%20or%20people%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20their%20student%20loans%20and%20they're%20just%20either%20choosing%20not%20to%2C%20or%20don't%20know%20they%20need%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20student-loan%20borrower%20typically%20enters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-default-repayment-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefault%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20not%20making%20payments%20for%20over%20270%20days.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20borrowers%20behind%20on%20payments%20were%20spared%20from%20garnishment%20and%20negative%20credit%20reporting%20due%20to%20a%20pause%20put%20in%20place%20by%20Trump%20and%20continued%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENegative%20credit%20reporting%20resumed%20in%20October%202024%2C%20and%20while%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20in%20early%20June%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-garnishment-paused-defaulted-student-loan-borrowers-trump-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epausing%20Social%20Security%20garnishment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wage%20garnishment%20will%20resume%20later%20this%20summer.%20The%20department%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20on%20a%20specific%20date%20that%20wage%20garnishment%20will%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2Fus-department-of-education-begin-federal-student-loan-collections-other-actions-help-borrowers-get-back-repayment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20that%20restarting%20collections%20will%20%26quot%3Bmove%20the%20federal%20student%20loan%20portfolio%20back%20into%20repayment%2C%20which%20benefits%20borrowers%20and%20taxpayers%20alike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurnbull%20said%20the%20economic%20implications%20of%20delinquency%20and%20default%20%E2%80%94%20including%20hits%20to%20credit%20scores%20and%20losing%20part%20of%20a%20paycheck%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20severe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20things%20that%2C%20I'm%20not%20only%20behind%20in%20paying%20on%20my%20student%20loan%2C%20but%20now%20my%20income%20stream%20is%20impacted%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Turnbull%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20compounding%20effect%20that%20consumers%20would%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d14348b-646c-4335-b91b-0d5e11311593%5C%22%3EOptions%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20to%20avoid%20default%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETurnbull%20said%20that%20problems%20start%20for%20borrowers%20behind%20on%20payments%20once%20their%20delinquent%20status%20is%20reported.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20their%20credit%20scores%20will%20decline%2C%20and%20it%20could%20immediately%20impact%20their%20abilities%20to%20get%20mortgages%2C%20competitive%20auto%20loan%20rates%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20just%20encourage%20anyone%20who%20has%20a%20student%20loan%2C%20is%20not%20paying%20on%20that%20now%2C%20and%20is%20confused%20or%20worried%20about%20where%20they're%20going%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20funds%2C%20don't%20wait%2C%26quot%3B%20Turnbull%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20wait%20until%20you%20get%20that%2090-day%20delinquency%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20your%20plan%20is%2C%20or%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20you're%20supposed%20to%20send%20your%20payment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20borrowers%20who%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estart%20a%20repayment%20plan%20are%20still%20struggling.%20Michael%20George%2C%2031%2C%20is%20in%20default%20on%20his%20student%20loans.%20He%20said%20he%20contacted%20Federal%20Student%20Aid's%20debt%20resolution%20group%20to%20begin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-defaulted-student-loan-borrowers-avoid-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloan%20rehabilitation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20requires%20a%20borrower%20to%20make%20nine%20payments%20within%2020%20days%20of%20the%20due%20date%20over%20a%20period%20of%2010%20consecutive%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Federal%20Student%20Aid's%20website%20said%20that%20wage%20garnishment%20will%20continue%20until%20a%20borrower%20makes%20at%20least%20five%20rehabilitation%20payments%2C%20George%20said%20his%20servicer%20gave%20him%20conflicting%20information%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eregarding%20the%20repayment%20schedule%20requirements%2C%20and%20he%20made%20payments%20that%20ended%20up%20not%20counting%20toward%20his%20rehabilitation%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20proper%20information%2C%20there's%20no%20consistency%2C%20there's%20no%20one%20streamlined%20black%20or%20white%20conciseness%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20literally%20feels%20like%20a%20dumpster%20fire%20of%20how%20rapid%20the%20announcement%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20loan%20rehabilitation%2C%20borrowers%20can%20also%20consolidate%20their%20defaulted%20student%20loan%20into%20a%20federal%20direct%20consolidation%20loan.%20While%20this%20option%20is%20quicker%20than%20loan%20rehabilitation%2C%20a%20key%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20record%20of%20the%20default%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20borrower's%20credit%20history.%20Borrowers%20can%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-get-new-path-to-discharge-debt-bankruptcy-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efile%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20process%20that%20was%20streamlined%20under%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-trump-voters-default-debt-collection-social-security-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eborrowers%20who%20voted%20for%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20they%20support%20efforts%20to%20collect%20student%20loans%2C%20the%20abrupt%20nature%20of%20the%20collections%20restart%20has%20sparked%20confusion%20and%20alarm%20among%20those%20in%20default%2C%20or%20at%20risk%20of%20defaulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fopinion%2Faccountability-returns-to-student-loans-forgiveness-borrower-debt-payment-9508da8d%3Fgaa_at%3Deafs%26gaa_n%3DASWzDAjor0ta7ZEVeLdYaxy8Q6AiCWQpkPN7K-cpl8GN9ibK5wNL5QpqLyZrjKPtlF0%253D%26gaa_ts%3D685d6e6e%26gaa_sig%3DfFZ9D9HPxb9CelKi9tBsQnw05eE7w2VFw3D_pbmDZUjSRoarwCjbthUNeMDxRAoKuvFMfjp3Syo1gBr5jUVIiQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20collections%20restart%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20unkind%20to%20student%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBorrowing%20money%20and%20failing%20to%20pay%20it%20back%20isn't%20a%20victimless%20offense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BDebt%20doesn't%20go%20away%3B%20it%20gets%20transferred%20to%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-lose-paychecks-wage-garnishment-default-debt-collections-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751311719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d490ff748d8c055f4664b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-lose-paychecks-wage-garnishment-default-debt-collections-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Millions%20of%20student%20loan%20borrowers%20are%20facing%20potential%20wage%20garnishment%20this%20summer%20if%20they%20don'