%20curling%20iron%20to%20get%20all%20the%20length%2C%26quot%3B%20Whately%20said.%20That%20full%20coverage%20is%20important%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20the%20heat%20can%20penetrate%20through%20each%20revolution%20of%20wound-up%20hair%20on%20a%20curling%20iron%20to%20create%20a%20lasting%20curl%20set.%26quot%3B%20Alternatively%2C%20shorter%20hair%20may%20want%20a%20thinner%20barrel%2C%20and%20thinner%20hair%20requires%20less%20intense%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tool's%20price%20tag%20is%20also%20worth%20noting.%20Whatley%20said%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20you%20get%20what%20you%20pay%20for.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20time%20when%20you're%20buying%20an%20inexpensive%20curling%20iron%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20a%20great%20result%20with%20the%20heating%20element%2C%26quot%3B%20Whatley%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20look%20for%20a%20curling%20iron%20that%20has%20a%20great%20heat%20element%20or%20a%20heating%20control%20that%20takes%20you%20from%20150%20degrees%20up%20to%20410%20degrees%20at%20least%2C%20and%20that%20determines%20the%20most%20appropriate%20heat%20setting%20on%20a%20curling%20iron%20depending%20on%20the%20hair%20texture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20curling%20irons%20we've%20tested%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109905168qt-20%26h%3D03629d232c145f80ca390d63a5739412bcc7ee2407420b7f21c9810b164cd35a%26postID%3D682cbfbd6d8149165ea00a9c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-curling-irons%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FNuMe-Octowand%252Fdp%252FB00KOUH9M8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENuMe%20Octowand%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20the%20top%20spot.%20It%20has%20multiple%20sizes%20and%20shapes%20of%20barrel%20attachments%2C%20so%20you%20essentially%20get%20eight%20curling%20irons%20in%20one%2C%20and%20it's%20incredibly%20easy%20for%20anyone%20from%20beginner%20to%20pro%20stylists%20to%20use.%20Below%20are%20more%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20curling%20irons%2C%20as%20well%20as%20answers%20to%20your%20most-asked%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211197c1e-7a4e-452e-a0f6-f9bdc176dd1f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20I%20test%20curling%20irons%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20test%20curling%20irons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20setting%20out%20to%20find%20the%20best%20curling%20irons%2C%20I%20established%20a%20list%20of%20criteria%20the%20tools%20would%20have%20to%20meet.%20The%20first%20was%20the%20temperature%20range%20%E2%80%94%20the%20more%20temperature%20options%2C%20the%20better%20users%20can%20control%20their%20styling%20experience.%20I%20also%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20quickly%20the%20irons%20heated%20up%20and%20cooled%20down%2C%20as%20well%20as%20whether%20they%20had%20an%20automatic%20shut-off%20feature.%20Barrel%20size%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20consideration%20(the%20size%20of%20the%20barrel%20determines%20the%20type%20of%20curl%20you're%20going%20to%20get)%2C%20and%20special%20features%20(unique%20technologies%2C%20barrel%20materials%2C%20interchangeable%20attachments%2C%20etc.)%20were%20also%20noted.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20styled%20my%20hair%20with%20each%20of%20them%20and%20took%20photos%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232e626f1-c98a-4536-be7b-ae9a65a7a387%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Why%20trust%20me%3F%5C%22%3EWhy%20trust%20me%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20beauty%20reporter%20and%20editor%20with%20over%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20experience%20testing%20hair%20products%2C%20I'm%20well-versed%20in%20the%20styling%20tools%20space.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20my%20hair%20has%20been%20cut%20to%20various%20lengths%2C%20so%20I%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20tools%20do%20and%20don't%20work%20for%20lengthy%20tresses%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20blunt%20bobs.%20That%20said%2C%20my%20strands%20are%20naturally%20wavy%20and%20they%20straighten%20easily%2C%20but%20don't%20always%20hold%20a%20curl.%20To%20ensure%20the%20tools%20I've%20crowned%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%20also%20work%20for%20other%20hair%20types%2C%20I%20combed%20through%20dozens%20of%20reviews%20on%20various%20websites%20and%20message%20boards%20for%20additional%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6377de5-a62b-40e2-9752-f6e8ca8db217%5C%22%3EOur%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20curling%20irons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Before%20and%20after%20of%20curling%20long%20straight%20hair%20with%20NuMe's%20curling%20iron%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6853162f85e81483682c6364%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20testing%20curling%20irons%2C%20I%20didn't%20use%20heat%20protectant%20sprays%20so%20I%20could%20see%20how%20dry%20my%20hair%20felt%20afterward.%20My%20strands%20are%20naturally%20quite%20dry%20with%20frizz%2C%20so%20they%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20holding%20a%20curl%2C%20but%20the%20NuMe%20was%20the%20most%20effective%20and%20had%20the%20best%20special%20features.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20crown%20the%20best%20curling%20iron%20overall%2C%20my%20criteria%20were%20as%20follows%3A%20Versatility%2C%20user-friendliness%2C%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%2C%20compatibility%20with%20different%20hair%20types%2C%20and%20heat%20adjustment.%20We%20tested%20some%20big%20names%20in%20this%20category%20%E2%80%94%20stylers%20like%20the%20Dyson%20Airwarp%20and%20Shark%20Beauty%20Flex%20%E2%80%94%20but%20when%20all%20was%20said%20and%20done%2C%20the%20NuMe%20Octowand%20is%20what%20checked%20all%20of%20our%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20base%20and%20eight%20attachments%20of%20various%20sizes%2C%20each%20of%20which%20creates%20a%20different%20style%20of%20curl.%20It's%20extremely%20easy%20to%20get%20the%20hang%20of%20%E2%80%94%20the%20attachments%20pop%20on%20and%20off%2C%20and%20the%20curling%20iron%20doesn't%20have%20a%20clamp%2C%20but%20comes%20with%20a%20glove%20that%20makes%20manual%20wrapping%20simple%20and%20safe.%20Plus%2C%20the%20tourmaline%20ceramic%20barrels%20are%20infused%20with%20far-infrared%20heat%20that%20dries%20hair%20from%20the%20inside%20out%20to%20prevent%20too%20much%20moisture%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20considering%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20also%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20on%20how%20users%20with%20hair%20types%20different%20from%20mine%20liked%20the%20product.%20This%20model%20was%20widely%20praised%20in%20reviews%20as%20being%20compatible%20with%20pretty%20much%20all%20hair%20types%20and%20lengths.%20You're%20essentially%20getting%20eight%20curling%20irons%20in%20one%2C%20for%20under%20%24175%20%E2%80%94%20an%20excellent%20value%20for%20anyone%20who%20is%20serious%20about%20daily%20styling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%20pick%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20Hot%20Tools%20Pro%20Artist%2024K%20Gold%20Extra%20Long%20Curling%20Iron%20on%20the%20left%20and%20after%20use%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862c58af748d8c055f4a695%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20Hot%20Tools%20Pro%20Artist%2024K%20Gold%20Extra%20Long%20Curling%20Iron%20(left)%20and%20after%20use%20(right).%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20many%20years%20testing%20hair%20tools%2C%20I've%20yet%20to%20try%20a%20Hot%20Tools%20styler%20that%20I%20didn't%20like%2C%20and%20the%2024K%20Gold%20Pro%20Artist%20Curling%20Iron%20is%20no%20exception.%20This%20pick%20is%20where%20I'd%20steer%20you%20if%20you%20told%20me%20you're%20not%20planning%20to%20curl%20your%20hair%20all%20that%20often%2C%20but%20you%20want%20an%20affordable%20tool%20that%20helps%20you%20get%20the%20job%20done%20for%20special%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20things%20I%20really%20like%20about%20this%20curling%20iron%20are%20its%20rest%20stand%20(an%20important%20feature%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20are%20clumsy%20and%20have%20knocked%20hot%20irons%20over%20before)%20and%20the%20easy-to-hold%20thumb%20grip%20on%20the%20handle.%20It%20also%20comes%20in%20various%20barrel%20widths%20up%20to%202%20inches%2C%20so%20you%20can%20choose%20what%20works%20best%20for%20your%20hair%20length.%20I%20tested%20the%202-inch%20barrel%2C%20but%20as%20someone%20with%20lengthy%20tresses%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20optimally%20suited%20for%20medium%20lengths%20because%20the%20barrel%20length%20isn't%20super%20long%20(which%20means%20you%20get%20fewer%20revolutions).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20this%20curling%20iron%20always%20results%20in%20a%20smooth%20finish%2C%20but%20don't%20expect%20many%20bells%20and%20whistles.%20It%20has%20a%20light-up%20on%2Foff%20switch%20and%20a%20temperature%20dial%20that%20makes%20for%20easy%20operation%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20extent%20of%20its%20special%20features.%20Though%20marketed%20as%20a%20pro%20tool%2C%20it's%20user-friendly%20for%20amateurs%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20beginners%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20before%20using%20the%20T3%20Curlwrap%20on%20the%20left%20and%20after%20use%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682cb7d73fe8d392836656dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20T3%20Curlwrap%20(left)%20and%20after%20use%20(right).%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20better%20curling%20iron%20to%20recommend%20to%20a%20beginner%20than%20a%20styling%20tool%20that%20does%20nearly%20half%20the%20work%20for%20you%3F%20The%20T3%20Curlwrap%20is%20a%20rotating%20tool%20that%20comes%20in%20two%20barrel%20sizes%3A%201-inch%20and%201.25-inch.%20It%20offers%20users%20nine%20adjustable%20heat%20settings%2C%20two%20timer%20settings%2C%20and%20two%20rotation%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20curling%20iron%20couldn't%20be%20easier%20to%20use.%20You'll%20place%20the%20bottom%20of%20a%20section%20of%20hair%20into%20the%20clamp%20per%20usual%2C%20but%20with%20a%20press%20of%20a%20button%2C%20the%20curling%20iron%20comes%20alive%20and%20twists%20just%20tight%20enough%20to%20create%20the%20perfect%20curl.%20Not%20only%20can%20you%20control%20how%20high%20you%20want%20to%20barrel%20to%20rotate%2C%20you%20can%20also%20set%20either%20a%205-%20or%208-second%20timer%20on%20the%20iron%20depending%20on%20how%20intense%20you%20want%20your%20curl%20to%20be%20(or%20how%20thin%20your%20hair%20is).%20When%20time's%20up%2C%20the%20iron%20alerts%20you%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20curl%3B%20however%2C%20you%20can%20keep%20the%20hair%20curling%20longer%20if%20you%20choose.%20This%20feature%20alone%20makes%20the%20iron%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20beginners%20who%20aren't%20sure%20how%20long%20to%20keep%20their%20strands%20spun%20around%20the%20barrel%2C%20or%20who%20don't%20have%20as%20much%20dexterity%20or%20experience%20with%20the%20curling%20motion.%20It's%20also%20a%20helpful%20detail%20for%20moms%20with%20little%20ones%20popping%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20bathroom%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20keep%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20to%20prevent%20heat%20damage%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20before%20using%20the%20Sutra%20IR2%20INFRARED%20Curling%20Iron%20on%20the%20left%20and%20during%20use%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682cb88dc6ad288d14816ccd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20Sutra%20IR2%20INFRARED%20Curling%20Iron%20(left)%20and%20during%20use%20(right).%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%2C%20over%20time%2C%20heat%20exposure%20does%20a%20number%20on%20your%20'do.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20are%20some%20precautions%20you%20can%20take%20to%20minimize%20the%20damage%2C%20like%20using%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-heat-protectant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20heat%20protectant%20sprays%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20some%20styling%20tools%20go%20the%20extra%20length%20to%20prevent%20heat%20damage%2C%20too.%20The%20Sutra%20IR2%20Infrared%20Curling%20Iron%2C%20for%20example%2C%20claims%20to%20prevent%20heat%20damage%20via%20its%20infrared%20heating%20technology%2C%20and%20we%20did%20a%20deep%20dive%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20isn't%20just%20marketing%20jargon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chicago-based%20bridal%20and%20celebrity%20hair%20stylist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmeganschnellhair%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMegan%20Schnell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20infrared%20technology%20won't%20eliminate%20moisture%20loss%20entirely%2C%20but%20it%20can%20minimize%20it%20by%20heating%20hair%20from%20the%20inside%20out%2C%20providing%20a%20%26quot%3Bgentler%2C%20more%20even%20heat%20that%20reduces%20damage%20to%20the%20outer%20cuticle.%26quot%3B%20So%20there%20is%20some%20truth%20to%20the%20technology's%20ability%20to%20maintain%20strand%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20also%20just%20a%20great%20curling%20iron%20that%20works%20for%20any%20hair%20type.%20It%20features%20a%20digital%20temperature-control%20system%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20add%20or%20subtract%20heat%20in%20seconds%20throughout%20your%20styling%20session%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20adjust%20heat%20quickly%20can%20also%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20preventing%20damaged%20strands.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20glove%20to%20safeguard%20your%20fingers%20from%20burns%20(a%20major%20plus%20for%20my%20butter%20fingers)%2C%20and%20has%20a%20rubber%20top%20to%20protect%20the%20scalp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20functionality%2C%20it%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20promise%20of%20being%20a%20one-pass%20iron.%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20tight%20curl%20the%201.3-inch%20barrel%20created%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20how%20healthy%20and%20shiny%20my%20hair%20looked%20after%20use%2C%20despite%20not%20having%20applied%20a%20heat%20protectant%20beforehand.%20This%20iron%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%2C%20left%20my%20hair%20looking%20totally%20smooth%20and%20frizz-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20long%20hair%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20before%20using%20the%20Bio%20Ionic%20Long%20Barrel%20Curling%20Iron%20on%20the%20left%20and%20after%20use%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682cb9913fe8d39283665716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20Bio%20Ionic%20Long%20Barrel%20Curling%20Iron%20(left)%20and%20after%20use%20(right).%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20often%20that%20I'm%20%26quot%3Bwowed%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20curling%20iron%2C%20but%20my%20long%20hair%20and%20I%20were%20thoroughly%20impressed%20by%20Bio%20Ionic's%20styler.%20The%20extra-long%20barrel%20length%20was%20key%20to%20achieving%20an%20even%20curl%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%20without%20having%20to%20do%20any%20extra%20twisting%20of%20the%20barrel.%20This%20is%20especially%20good%20news%20for%20anyone%20who%20deals%20with%20the%20dreaded%20little%20crimp%20that%20can%20happen%20when%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20slipping%20a%20long%20section%20of%20hair%20through%20the%20clamp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iron%20uses%20an%20ionic%20technology%20that%20seals%20hair%20cuticles%20to%20reduce%20frizz%20and%20breaks%20water%20molecules%20into%20very%20small%20particles%20for%20faster%20styling.%20So%20not%20only%20does%20this%20longer%20styling%20tool%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20manage%20long%20hair%20and%20style%20pieces%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%2C%20but%20it%20also%20helps%20to%20minimize%20the%20impact%20of%20heat%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20even%20considering%20its%20extra%20inches%2C%20Bio%20Ionic's%20curling%20iron%20remains%20lightweight%20and%20easy%20to%20hold%20securely%20because%20of%20its%20cool-touch%20grip.%20Just%20be%20warned%3A%20The%20iron%20comes%20with%20plastic%20on%20the%20plates%2C%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20take%20that%20off%20before%20turning%20the%20heat%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20beach%20waves%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20before%20using%20the%20Beachwaver%20Pro%20on%20the%20left%20and%20after%20use%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682cbaa568a292900801cf49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20hair%20before%20using%20the%20Beachwaver%20Pro%20(left)%20and%20after%20use%20(right).%3Cp%3EJulia%20Guerra%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20Beachwaver%20since%20I%20first%20got%20my%20hands%20on%20the%20iron%20in%202015%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy%20that%20even%2010%20years%20later%2C%20its%20products%20still%20stand.%20The%201.5-inch%20barrel%20size%20is%20what%20helps%20you%20achieve%20a%20chunky%20curl.%20To%20get%20that%20coveted%20just-off-the-beach%20wave%2C%20I%20softly%20glide%20my%20fingers%20through%20and%20break%20up%20pieces%20of%20hair%20for%20vacation-coded%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20self-rotating%20curling%20iron%20is%20user-friendly%2C%20making%20it%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20beginners%20who%20want%20bigger%20waves.%20You%20simply%20open%20the%20clamp%20and%20secure%20your%20strands%20near%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20hair%2C%20select%20either%20%26quot%3BL%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BR%26quot%3B%20to%20let%20the%20iron%20know%20which%20side%20of%20the%20hair%20you're%20curling%2C%20and%20then%20press%20the%20%26quot%3BGo%26quot%3B%20button%20to%20start%20its%20rotation.%20After%20waiting%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20glide%20the%20barrel%20down%20to%20reveal%20the%20curl%20and%20comb%20your%20fingers%20through%20your%20strands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeatures%20worth%20highlighting%20include%20the%20curling%20iron's%20rest%20stand%2C%20its%2030-second%20heat-up%20time%2C%20and%20a%20decent-length%20barrel%20long%20enough%20to%20curl%20medium%20to%20long%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarrel%20size%20and%20material%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20curling%20iron%20for%20your%20hair%20type%2C%20remember%20that%20barrel%20sizes%20determine%20the%20type%20of%20curl%20a%20tool%20can%20create.%20For%20example%2C%20Whatley%20recommends%20a%20larger%20barrel%20%E2%80%94%201.5%20or%202%20inches%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20a%20larger%20curl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20terms%20of%20heat%2C%20there%20are%20two%20things%20to%20consider%3A%20First%2C%20curling%20irons%20(and%20any%20heat%20styling%20tool)%20with%20a%20range%20of%20heat%20settings%20give%20users%20more%20control%20over%20their%20strands'%20heat%20exposure.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20iron%20feels%20too%20hot%2C%20you%20can%20adjust.%20That%20said%2C%20heat%20directly%20correlates%20to%20the%20type%20of%20curl%20you%20can%20create.%20According%20to%20Whatley%2C%20the%20hair%20creates%20a%20professionally%20set%20curl%20at%20350%20to%20400%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20Thinner%20hair%20may%20benefit%20from%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20that%20temperature%20setting%20to%20avoid%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20can%20I%20get%20salon-curled%20hair%20at%20home%3F%3Cp%3EIt%20always%20comes%20down%20to%20prep%20and%20products%20when%20styling%20hair.%20According%20to%20professional%20hair%20and%20makeup%20artist%20Kate%20Johnson%2C%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.glossed.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlossed%20Finishing%20Studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebridalbeautyteam.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Bridal%20Beauty%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mastering%20a%20salon%20curl%20at%20home%20is%20no%20exception.%20The%20first%20step%2C%20Johnson%20says%2C%20is%20to%20wash%20and%20blow-dry%20your%20hair%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20heat%20protectant%20that%20has%20styling%20qualities%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109905168qt-20%26h%3D0eaa0690244df7f852c73b542befc4c7c084234582ef357d07f5c0bd384ff596%26postID%3D682cbfbd6d8149165ea00a9c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-curling-irons%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sephora.com%252Fproduct%252Fprotect-prevent-spray-P432032%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoroccan%20Oil%20Protect%20and%20Prevent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20gives%20you%20shine%2C%20but%20also%20isn't%20heavy%20and%20allows%20bounce%20and%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BShorter%20hair%20has%20less%20weight%2C%20so%20it%20will%20hold%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20answer%20is%20simply%20a%20matter%20of%20technique.%20Getting%20the%20hang%20of%20how%20you%20like%20your%20hair%20sectioned%2C%20parted%2C%20and%20what%20direction%20you%20prefer%20your%20curls%20makes%20a%20big%20difference.%20Next%20time%20you're%20at%20the%20salon%2C%20ask%20your%20stylist%20for%20some%20guidance.%20Identify%20how%20much%20hair%20to%20section%20out%2C%20and%20ask%20what%20strategy%20they%20use%20to%20curl%20hair%20like%20yours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20size%20barrel%20should%20you%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20barrel%20size%20you%20use%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20type%20of%20curl%20you're%20looking%20to%20create.%20For%20a%20tool%20with%20maximum%20versatility%2C%20Tom%20Smith%2C%20celebrity%20hairstylist%20and%20International%20Creative%2FColour%20Director%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.evohair.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20smaller%20barrel%20sizes%20will%20give%20you%20more%20options.%20For%20a%20loose%20or%20undone%20texture%2C%20Smith%20says%20a%20barrel%20that%20measures%2032mm%20or%20above%20is%20best.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20temperature%20is%20best%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20adding%20a%20hot%20tool%20to%20the%20hair%2C%20the%20hair%20will%20start%20to%20create%20a%20set%20at%20350%20degrees%20that%20will%20hold%20as%20a%20professional%20curl%2C%26quot%3B%20Whatley%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20recommend%20not%20going%20any%20higher%20than%20a%20350%20degrees%20to%20a%20400%20degrees%20temperature%20to%20get%20that%20perfect%20set.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20better%20to%20curl%20hair%20with%20a%20curling%20iron%20or%20a%20straightener%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20says%20that%20curling%20irons%20are%20better%20to%20curl%20hair%20with%20than%20straighteners%20because%20the%20latter%20%26quot%3Bsmash%20the%20cuticle%20of%20the%20hair%20vs%20bending%20it.%26quot%3B%20Plus%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20%5Ba%20straightener%5D%20that%20has%20a%20beveled%20edge%20still%20squeezes%20the%20hair%20between%20two%20flat%20plates%2C%20which%20will%20reduce%20volume%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20make%20curls%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secret%2C%20Johnson%20says%2C%20isn't%20necessarily%20how%20you%20%3Cem%3Ecurl%3C%2Fem%3E%20your%20hair%2C%20but%20how%20you%20%3Cem%3Ecool%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20pos