ntelligence%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe're%20going%20to%20call%20our%20overall%20organization%20Meta%20Superintelligence%20Labs%20(MSL).%20This%20includes%20all%20of%20our%20foundations%2C%20product%2C%20and%20FAIR%20teams%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20new%20lab%20focused%20on%20developing%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20models.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlexandr%20Wang%20has%20joined%20Meta%20to%20serve%20as%20our%20Chief%20AI%20Officer%20and%20lead%20MSL.%20Alex%20and%20I%20have%20worked%20together%20for%20several%20years%2C%20and%20I%20consider%20him%20to%20be%20the%20most%20impressive%20founder%20of%20his%20generation.%20He%20has%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20the%20historic%20importance%20of%20superintelligence%2C%20and%20as%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20he%20built%20ScaleAI%20into%20a%20fast-growing%20company%20involved%20in%20the%20development%20of%20almost%20all%20leading%20models%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENat%20Friedman%20has%20also%20joined%20Meta%20to%20partner%20with%20Alex%20to%20lead%20MSL%2C%20heading%20our%20work%20on%20AI%20products%20and%20applied%20research.%20Nat%20will%20work%20with%20Connor%20to%20define%20his%20role%20going%20forward.%20He%20ran%20GitHub%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20has%20run%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20AI%20investment%20firms.%20Nat%20has%20served%20on%20our%20Meta%20Advisory%20Group%20for%20the%20last%20year%2C%20so%20he%20already%20has%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20our%20roadmap%20and%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20also%20have%20several%20strong%20new%20team%20members%20joining%20today%20or%20who%20have%20joined%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20that%20I'm%20excited%20to%20share%20as%20well%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETrapit%20Bansal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20pioneered%20RL%20on%20chain%20of%20thought%20and%20co-creator%20of%20o-series%20models%20at%20OpenAI