20my%20left%20hand%20had%20now%20spread%20all%20over%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20been%20given%20an%20electric%20shock.%20The%20LAD%20artery%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20three%20most%20important%20coronary%20arteries%20in%20the%20body%2C%20was%20completely%20blocked%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20mentioned%20post-surgery%20that%20what%20I%20had%20experienced%20was%20a%20major%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImmense%20pain%20during%20the%20surgery%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20pain%20I%20experienced%20all%20through%20is%20not%20something%20that%20I%20can%20even%20put%20in%20words.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20about%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20post-surgery%20that%20I%20felt%20some%20kind%20of%20relief%20from%20the%20pain.%20There%20were%20two%20stents%20that%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20LAD%20artery%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20angiography%20was%20done%2C%20there%20were%20other%20blockages%20also%20that%20were%20found.%20I%20had%20almost%2095%20per%20cent%20blockages%20in%20other%20arteries%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20I%20was%20advised%20to%20go%20through%20yet%20another%20angioplasty%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20fix%20those%20blockages%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20surgeries%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20various%20medications%2C%20and%20I%20pop%20in%20at%20least%20ten%20pills%20a%20day%20now.%20From%20medicines%20for%20blood%20pressure%20to%20cholesterol%20and%20blood%20thinners%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prescribed%20so%20many.%20None%20of%20which%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20pre-surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EI%20was%20fairly%20fit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20overweight.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20lean%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20my%20BMI%20was%2025%20%E2%80%94%20well%20within%20what%E2%80%99s%20considered%20the%20normal%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%