ohit%20says%2C%C2%A0%20provides%20detailed%20insights%20into%20consumption%20trends%2C%20helping%20users%20track%20their%20habits%20and%20encouraging%20a%20culture%20of%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20employing%20these%20intelligent%20devices%2C%20residents%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20alter%20their%20behaviour%20to%20prevent%20unnecessary%20water%20use.%20The%20ability%20to%20pinpoint%20leaks%20and%20inefficient%20use%20within%20households%20or%20larger%20complexes%20means%20potential%20issues%20can%20be%20resolved%20before%20they%20escalate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rohit%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AI-enabled%20smart%20metres%20and%20dynamic%20billing%20cut%20water%20bills%20by%2055%20percent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-3-1750998948-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-456822%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20AI-enabled%20smart%20metres%20and%20dynamic%20billing%20reduce%20water%20bills%20by%2055%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReducing%20water%20bills%20to%20half%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rohit%E2%80%99s%20smart%20water%20systems%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20manage%20their%20water%20use%20without%20the%20hassle.%20By%20automating%20the%20process%2C%20he%20has%20helped%20families%20waste%20less%20water%20and%20save%20a%20lot%20more%20on%20their%20monthly%20bills.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20Agua%E2%80%99s%20smart%20water%20metres%20are%20installed%20in%20over%20450%20flats%20across%20Bengaluru.%20The%20results%20have%20been%20encouraging.%20Apartment%20complexes%20using%20the%20system%20have%20reduced%20their%20overall%20water%20consumption%20by%2035%20percent%20and%20monthly%20water%20bills%20by%20more%20than%2055%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-based%20Ranjan%20Prakash%20remembers%20how%20things%20were%20back%20in%202016.%20There%20were%20constant%20arguments%20about%20water%20being%20wasted%20and%20society%20maintenance%20charges%20going%20up%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20because%20tanker%20water%20had%20become%20so%20expensive.%20It%20affected%20everyone%20in%20the%20community%2C%20whether%20they%20were%20families%20or%20bachelors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20issue%2C%20his%20society%20installed%20Agua%E2%80%99s%20smart%20water%20metres%20for%20household-level%20monitoring.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20installing%20the%20smart%20meters%2C%20our%20water%20use%20became%20sustainable%20and%20we%20even%20saw%20a%20reduction%20in%20our%20family%E2%80%99s%20water%20bills.%20For%20a%20monthly%20rental%20of%20Rs%20100%2C%20the%20metres%20gave%20us%20real-time%20usage%20tracking%2C%20water%20level%20notifications%2C%20and%20alerts%20for%20significant%20consumption%20changes%2C%20along%20with%20transparent%20billing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20within%20three%20months%2C%20the%20community%20reduced%20water%20consumption%20by%2030%20percent%20and%20cut%20costs%20by%20over%2045%20percent.%20We%20became%20less%20dependent%20on%20expensive%20tanker%20deliveries%20and%20used%20borewell%20sources%20mor